struct.exostring: If character is female, nothing happens

Sarna initiates conversation when player enters the Sith party apartment
Dialog mission statement:
Female players can speak to Sarna and through persuasion and paying credits convince her to arrange for them to get invited to a party where they can steal her keycard.
Male players can flirt with her and use persuasion to get invited to a party where they can steal her keycard.
Exit points:
1. Player at party, Sarna initiates conversation, fade to black and come back with everyone drunk and passed out. Player can loot body of keycard.
2. Player bribed Sarna, he leaves are to arrange party, mark party apartment on map.
3. Nothing happens
4. Nothing happens.
5. Nothing happens.
6. Player rejected, nothing else happens
7. Player rejected, nothing else happens
8. Player invited to party.
escape area, go to party house.
Fade to black, come back and everyone is passed out on the floor. Player can loot the sleeping bodies.
